## 共通化アプローチ

### 1. **Custom Hook を作成する方法（推奨）**

`useSubmitGuard` のようなカスタムフックを作成：

```typescript
// web/src/hooks/useSubmitGuard.ts
import { useState, useCallback } from 'react';

export const useSubmitGuard = () => {
  const [isSubmitting, setIsSubmitting] = useState(false);

  const executeWithGuard = useCallback(async <T>(
    fn: () => Promise<T>
  ): Promise<T | null> => {
    if (isSubmitting) {
      return null;
    }

    setIsSubmitting(true);
    try {
      return await fn();
    } finally {
      setIsSubmitting(false);
    }
  }, [isSubmitting]);

  return { isSubmitting, executeWithGuard };
};

// 使い方
const { isSubmitting, executeWithGuard } = useSubmitGuard();

const createPlayer = async () => {
  await executeWithGuard(async () => {
    // 処理内容
  });
};
```

### 2. **Higher Order Component (HOC) を使う方法**

```typescript
// web/src/components/hoc/withSubmitGuard.tsx
export const withSubmitGuard = <P extends object>(
  Component: React.ComponentType<P>
) => {
  return (props: P) => {
    const [isSubmitting, setIsSubmitting] = useState(false);

    return (
      <Component 
        {...props} 
        isSubmitting={isSubmitting}
        setIsSubmitting={setIsSubmitting}
      />
    );
  };
};
```

### 3. **ボタンコンポーネントを拡張する方法**

```typescript
// web/src/components/common/SubmitButton.tsx
export const SubmitButton: FC<{
  onClick: () => Promise<void>;
  children: ReactNode;
  // その他の Button props
}> = ({ onClick, children, ...rest }) => {
  const [isSubmitting, setIsSubmitting] = useState(false);

  const handleClick = async () => {
    if (isSubmitting) return;

    setIsSubmitting(true);
    try {
      await onClick();
    } finally {
      setIsSubmitting(false);
    }
  };

  return (
    <Button
      {...rest}
      loading={isSubmitting}
      disabled={isSubmitting}
      onClick={handleClick}
    >
      {children}
    </Button>
  );
};
```

### 4. **既存の `wrapForLoading` を拡張する方法**

```typescript
// web/src/utils/functions/transformer.ts に追加
export const wrapForLoadingWithGuard = async <T>(
  setIsSubmitting: (isSubmitting: boolean) => void,
  getIsSubmitting: () => boolean,
  fn: () => Promise<T>
): Promise<T | null> => {
  if (getIsSubmitting()) {
    return null;
  }

  setIsSubmitting(true);
  try {
    return await fn();
  } finally {
    setIsSubmitting(false);
  }
};
```

## 推奨アプローチ

**Custom Hook（方法 1）**が最も推奨される理由：
- ✅ React のベストプラクティスに準拠
- ✅ 既存コードへの影響が最小限
- ✅ テストが容易
- ✅ 再利用性が高い
- ✅ 型安全性を保てる

この方法で実装しますか？

